---
Language:        C
# Uses the standard LLVM style (VS Code Default)
BasedOnStyle:    LLVM

# Keeps your preferred indentation of 4 spaces (Standard LLVM uses 2, but 4 is common in C)
IndentWidth:     4
TabWidth:        4
UseTab:          Never

# This ensures braces follow the standard LLVM rules (usually attached)
# We removed "BreakBeforeBraces: Linux" to stop K&R style

# Prevent long lines from breaking (Your main requirement)
ColumnLimit:     0
...